e-mail: Ron_St.John@hc-sc.gc.ca
[Canada appears to suffer from the same problem as other federal countries
like the USA (see Plague - USA: Reporting 981025160553) in getting rapid
reports of internationally notifiable diseases from its provinces. In our
opinion there should be no excuse for delay in this electronic age - Mod.JW
